        <Parent_String>election districts [300000709], administrative districts [300000707], districts by function [300000706], districts [300000705], Built Complexes and Districts (hierarchy name) [300000201], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
