    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Electoral constituencies that elect one member of a congress. In the United States, territorial divisions of a state from which a member of the United States House of Representatives is elected. Other nations having congressional districts are the Philippines and Japan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046693/Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary [online] (1997-2002)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>遴選一名國會議員的選區。在美國，則是意指選出各州眾議院議員的土地區域。其他有國會選區的國家為菲律賓與日本。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wahlkreis, der ein Kongressmitglied wählt. In den Vereinigten Staaten von Amerika bezeichnet der Begriff das territoriale Teilgebiet eines Staates, aus dem ein Mitglied des Repräsentantenhauses der Vereinigten Staaten gewählt wird. Andere Nationen mit Kongresswahlbezirken sind die Philippinen und Japan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
